# ============================================================
# NiveshNarrator — Cursor Rules  (v2 — audited & gap-fixed)
# Automated Indian Retirement Planning Video Pipeline
# ============================================================
# These rules are authoritative for EVERY file in this repo.
# Follow them exactly. Never debate or reinterpret them.
# ============================================================

## PROJECT OVERVIEW

NiveshNarrator generates original retirement planning videos for Indian
white-collar professionals (age 35–50).
  NiveshNarrator = Nivesh (investment, Hindi) + Narrator (AI voiceover)

Every video is 100% original — generated persona, deterministic math,
Hinglish script via Claude Sonnet, ElevenLabs voiceover, FFmpeg video,
YouTube long-form + Instagram Reels upload.

Pipeline stages (strict order):
  GENERATE → CALCULATE → WRITE → REVIEW (human gate) → PRODUCE → PUBLISH → FEEDBACK

Revenue: YouTube AdSense Education CPM ₹300–420 + fintech brand deals + affiliate.
Target: 1,000+ unique video scenarios before parameter exhaustion.
Post-exhaustion: new series (salary slip, tax optimisation, home loan prepayment).

