  North (Delhi, Lucknow, Chandigarh, Jaipur): Sharma, Gupta, Verma, Singh, Yadav…
  South (Chennai, Hyderabad, Bengaluru, Kochi): Krishnan, Nair, Reddy, Rao, Pillai…
