## COMMON FAILURES AND EXACT FIXES

| Failure | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| ElevenLabs file < 50KB | Empty body despite HTTP 200 | Retry immediately; check elevenlabs.io/status |
| Chart is solid black PNG | `matplotlib.use("Agg")` not on line 1 | Move to absolute first line before all other imports |
| Shorts video is 62 seconds | Voiceover ran long | Shorten script to 130–145 words; add assertion |
| YouTube `invalid_grant` | OAuth token expired (7 days) | Re-run OAuth2 flow; refresh youtube_token.json |
| Instagram stuck in PROCESSING | Wrong codec (VP9 or HEVC) | Confirm `-c:v libx264 -c:a aac` in shorts_composer.py |
| `DisclaimerMissingError` | Claude omitted SEBI disclaimer | Check logs/write.log for full prompt; fix system prompt; manually regenerate |
| `PersonaExhaustedError` | All param combinations used | Expected — start new series (salary, tax, home loan) |
| `PersonaNearDuplicateError` too aggressive | Threshold too low | Raise `NEAR_DUPLICATE_THRESHOLD` to 0.90 in .env |
| Numbers wrong in script | `NumberAccuracyError` not firing | Check `script_validator.py` — verify `format_inr()` output matches script |
| Section 87A rebate not applied | Missing rebate logic in take_home.py | Add: if taxable_income ≤ 700000 → set tax = 0 |
| Overlays not appearing | Digit string matching attempted | Switch to `words_to_inr_phrase()` + SequenceMatcher ≥ 0.70 |

---

## HARD LIMITS — PERMANENT, NON-NEGOTIABLE CONSTRAINTS

1.  **SAFE_WITHDRAWAL_RATE = 0.033** — NEVER 0.04 (India CPI is 6%, not 3%)
2.  **EPF compounds ANNUALLY** — NEVER monthly (EPFO end-of-year accounting)
3.  **Human review is MANDATORY** — no skip flag, no override, no exception
4.  **Claude Sonnet only** for scripts — NEVER Haiku or any other model
5.  **`DisclaimerMissingError` NEVER auto-retried** — investigate system prompt
6.  **Both SEBI flags must be True before upload** — UploadError if either False
7.  **ASCI affiliate disclosure NEVER removed** — legally required under Indian law
8.  **`pipeline/calculate/` NEVER makes external calls** — pure Python only
9.  **`annotationClickThroughRate` NEVER used** — deprecated, returns empty data
10. **`title_card.py` → 1080×960 PNG** (video top panel) ≠ **`thumbnail.py` → 1280×720 JPG** (YouTube preview)
11. **Business logic NEVER in `dashboard.py`** — always in `actions.py`
12. **`matplotlib.use("Agg")` MUST be absolute line 1** — before any matplotlib import
13. **EPF rate NEVER hardcoded** — always `settings.EPF_RATE` from `.env`
14. **Shorts script generated ONLY after long-form APPROVED** — status gate enforced
15. **Section 87A rebate MUST be applied** — if taxable_income ≤ ₹7L, tax = 0
16. **`content_id` is UUIDv4** — generated in `persona.py`, prefix on every log line

---

## BUILD ORDER  (strict — each stage gates the next)

```
Stage 0 : Scaffold         → __init__.py everywhere, empty modules, no syntax errors
                             logs/ created, assets/sebi/ files present
Stage 1 : Core             → exceptions → logger → models → utils → config → database
                             ✅ pytest tests/test_core.py GREEN
Stage 2 : Math Engine      → take_home → corpus → epf → nps → savings → sip
                             → pension → validator
                             ✅ pytest tests/test_golden.py GREEN before continuing
                             ✅ pytest tests/test_math_validator.py GREEN
Stage 3 : Persona Gen      → names → deduplicator → persona
Stage 4 : Script Writing   → scriptwriter → script_validator → hook_validator
                             → shorts_writer → title_generator
                             ✅ pytest tests/test_script_validator.py GREEN
Stage 5 : Review Dashboard → actions.py (full logic + tests) → dashboard.py (UI)
Stage 6 : Media Production → tts → tts_shorts → charts → chart_validator
                             → overlays → title_card → thumbnail
                             → composer → shorts_composer → branding
Stage 7 : Publish          → formatter → uploader (with SEBI gate) → retry
Stage 8 : Feedback/Storage → analytics → s3 → cleanup → db_logger
                             → sentry → metrics → health
Stage 9 : Orchestrator     → recalculate_math.py → export_analytics.py
                             → orchestrator.py → main.py CLI
Stage 10: Final            → ✅ pytest tests/ -v --tb=short ALL GREEN
                             ✅ python main.py --run-cycle --dry-run PASSES
                             ✅ Log ends with "dry_run=True — skipping upload"
```

